title: Vóta 2024
overview: TG4 is delighted to present Vóta 2024, a comprehensive two-day live event covering the results and detailed analysis of this year's general election. Hosted by Siún Nic Gearailt and Eimear Ní Chonaola, these special broadcasts will bring viewers expert insights, live result updates, and in-depth commentary as the nation charts its political future.
